{
  "stem": "23096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This one barn-- like I was telling you about-- this one man, it's-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] of all-- it's-- it's-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard to say-- you ignored the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this one was the one that got my attention.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- You would think that they would have been overjoyed to see us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then you wonder, did they even know who we were?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were their minds gone?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were their other human capabilities-- they were so-- so-- so close to death that you wonder sometimes what they were even thinking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know other places, they say when they came in, they were overjoyed, and-- and ran around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when you see something where people don't do much-- of course, in this camp it was a little bit different, because the only ones left there supposedly were dead or had been-- had been shot just before the-- the Germans pulled out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So maybe they were too far gone to be-- to be happy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you always wonder, did any of them make it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I sure hope so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you-- do you recall what the date was when you entered the camp?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the exact date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about the-- the 1st-- almost the-- about the 1st of April.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I know-- if it was the first, second, third, something-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eisenhower didn't go in until-- [SIGHS] I think the 11th or 12th.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after the reports-- of course, when-- after we-- you know, we were working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we weren't infantry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a job to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we had to get this telephone line in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
